description: Deletes the specified API key. The API key must have been deactivated more than 90 days previously.

parameters.name: KeyName
parameters.description: The name of the API key to delete.

parameters.name: ForceDelete
parameters.description: ForceDelete bypasses an API key's expiry conditions and deletes the key. Set the parameter true to delete the key or to false to not preemptively delete the API key. Valid values: true, or false. Required: No.
